data.text:
Engineering & ConstructionIndustrial Services

SIGA Ingeniería y Consultoría SA provides consulting and engineering services. It offers management and project management services, technical inspection of works, mining and geotechnics, environmental management and contract management, and developing projects and studies in different sectors of development. The company was founded by Luis Alberto Olcay Cárdenas and Juan Carlos Olcay Cárdenas in 1996 and is headquartered in Ñuñoa, Chile.
